for why you were kissing Jessi!

616
00:34:42,541 --> 00:34:43,353
There is.

617
00:34:43,453 --> 00:34:45,142
I'll tell you everything.

618
00:34:45,242 --> 00:34:47,707
I don't even care anymore,
because none of it matters.

619
00:34:47,807 --> 00:34:49,191
It does matter.

620
00:34:49,522 --> 00:34:52,047
