rental for another three weeks.

638
00:36:20,393 --> 00:36:21,262
Sweetie.

639
00:36:21,889 --> 00:36:22,859
I'm sorry.

640
00:36:26,521 --> 00:36:28,281
I know you're frustrated.

641
00:36:29,308 --> 00:36:31,030
