was telling Andy about it.

646
00:36:43,230 --> 00:36:44,007
I just

647
00:36:44,771 --> 00:36:45,892
really miss her.

648
00:36:49,085 --> 00:36:50,589
The Jessi thing,

649
00:36:51,158 --> 00:36:53,031
you know it's not gonna be easy, right?

650
00:36:53,131 --> 00:36:56,062
<i>I know we all got used to Kyle
and that turned out great.</i>

651
00:36:56,162 --> 00:36:58,404
<i>I just hope we can get used to her.</i>

652
00:36:59,694 --> 00:37:00,653
