Do anything exciting?

656
00:37:12,058 --> 00:37:13,188
Not really, no.

657
00:37:13,447 --> 00:37:16,303
How about I phrase it this way.
See anyone exciting?

658
00:37:16,403 --> 00:37:18,810
Actually, no, Dad, I didn't.
And thank you, Jessi.

659
00:37:18,910 --> 00:37:20,614
