715
00:42:40,762 --> 00:42:41,663
<i>And now,</i>

716
00:42:42,063 --> 00:42:44,611
<i>somehow our connection
had been severed.</i>

717
00:43:06,569 --> 00:43:08,869
<i>Though she had never
played better,</i>

718
00:43:08,969 --> 00:43:12,415
